TI  - Uncovering the Landscape of Participatory Research in Agricultural Innovation: A Scoping Review
T2  - CITIZEN SCIENCE-THEORY AND PRACTICE
LA  - English
KW  - innovative agricultural practices
KW  - co-innovation
KW  - participatory methodologies
KW  - stakeholder engagement
