TI  - Building adaptive capacity in rural Namibia Community information toolkits on climate change
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF CLIMATE CHANGE STRATEGIES AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Adaptation
