TI  - Talking as friends: Weaving local and scientific knowledge to co-produce an integrated index to assess rangeland multifunctionality in a dryland Biosphere Reserve in Mexico
T2  - PEOPLE AND NATURE
LA  - English
KW  - Biosphere Reserve
KW  - knowledge co-production
