TI  - Assessment of behavioural response to climate forecasts and climate change adaptation by small-holder farmers in Nambale sub-county of Busia county, Kenya
T2  - PHYSICS AND CHEMISTRY OF THE EARTH
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change adaptation
