TI  - Understanding constraints to adaptation using a community-centred toolkit
T2  - PHILOSOPHICAL TRANSACTIONS OF THE ROYAL SOCIETY B-BIOLOGICAL SCIENCES
LA  - English
KW  - adaptive capacity
KW  - natural resource use
