TI  - Integrating social dynamics in the participatory modeling of small-scale cattle farmers' perceptions and responses to climate variability in the Yucatan Peninsula, Mexico
T2  - FRONTIERS IN SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - social dynamics
