TI  - Ineffective Agricultural Advisors (AAs) Support on Climate Information and Adaptation Strategies Dissemination in Ugu District, KwaZulu-Natal
T2  - SAGE OPEN
LA  - English
KW  - agricultural advisors
KW  - capacity building
