TI  - Farmer field schools, climate action plans and climate change resilience among smallholder farmers in Northern Ghana
T2  - CLIMATIC CHANGE
LA  - English
KW  - Climate Resilience
KW  - Farmer Field Schools
KW  - Climate Action Plans
KW  - Resilience theory
KW  - Smallholder Farmers
KW  - Ghana
KW  - IMPACT
