TI  - Assessment of indigenous knowledge and technology used for climate adaptation and resilience in coastal area of Bangladesh
T2  - DISCOVER ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - WATER SCARCITY
KW  - VULNERABILITY
KW  - SALINITY
