TI  - Adoption of climate change mitigation and adaptation strategies among smallholder farmers in African countries: a systematic review
T2  - DISCOVER SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - Access to credit
KW  - Agroforestry
KW  - Climate-Smart agriculture (CSA)
KW  - Indigenous knowledge
KW  - Global warming
