TI  - The Perceived Impact of Climate Change on the Livelihoods of Smallholder Farmers in Kwazulu-Natal Province, South Africa
T2  - SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - climate change
KW  - smallholder farmers
KW  - Sustainable Livelihood Framework
