TI  - Exploring the concept of place in the literature on smallholder farmers and climate change adaptation in Sub-Saharan Africa
T2  - SOUTH AFRICAN GEOGRAPHICAL JOURNAL
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change adaptation
KW  - location
KW  - locale
KW  - sense of place
KW  - smallholder farmers
