TI  - Do Zambian farmers manage climate risks?
T2  - APPLIED ECONOMIC PERSPECTIVES AND POLICY
LA  - English
KW  - agriculture
KW  - mediation analysis
KW  - self-insurance
KW  - weather risk
KW  - Zambia
