TI  - Sustainability responses to climate-smart adaptation in Africa: implication for food security among farm households in the Central Region of Ghana
T2  - AFRICAN JOURNAL OF ECONOMIC AND MANAGEMENT STUDIES
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Adaptive capacity
KW  - Sustainability index
