TI  - Crop switching as an adaptation strategy to climate change: the case of Semien Shewa Zone of Ethiopia
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF CLIMATE CHANGE STRATEGIES AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Crop switching
