TI  - Assessing the impact of climate-resilient maize varieties and their interaction with the stem borer chilo partellus (swinhoe) (lepidoptera: crambidae) in semi-field conditions
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF TROPICAL INSECT SCIENCE
